{"tid":822243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今次李嘉誠終於頂唔住[教育局宣布明天全部學校停課]","createTime":"2018-09-16T08:35:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T10:05:05.000Z","uid":208748,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4f9928e060d6342d016072a77a987cd695b066be","tid":822243,"uid":208748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:35:56.000Z","msg":"強颱風「山竹」襲港，教育局指，考慮到社區各項設施需時清理和維修，為確保學生安全，教育局宣布明日（17日）無論是否仍有熱帶氣旋警告信號及暴雨警告信號發出，所有學校均停課。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學校應根據既定的緊急應變措施指引，在安全情況下保持校舍開放，並安排人手在校內安全的地方照顧有確切需要回校的學生，家長應考慮家居、附近的道路、區內天氣、學生的照顧等因素決定是否送子女會回校。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180916/s00001/1537086087627\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180916%2Fs00001%2F1537086087627&d=oKxhwpfRMxZjXWLFL2Yh9pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=0c5c12b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180916%2Fs00001%2F1537086087627&h=5cd0c95d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180916/s00001/1537086087627</a>"},{"pid":"8d1e7311e27034a4b131af448112005a2f582b85","tid":822243,"uid":204700,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:37:10.000Z","msg":"大專算唔算學校"},{"pid":"fe571de36b9e25f9f7551799b9dd787b62778407","tid":822243,"uid":153114,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:37:35.000Z","msg":"大學都停？"},{"pid":"7065c2b2eaf3e6185ddbde2b5c2803ce1e1f5bb8","tid":822243,"uid":1373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:38:00.000Z","msg":"大學冇停"},{"pid":"2e37b41f345eefa8fed9d767b15b5550376919c2","tid":822243,"uid":96871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:38:34.000Z","msg":"退左休啦"},{"pid":"cbf25e5206e285041cf3136199fc31e531cd2e61","tid":822243,"uid":75196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"